{"root":{"data":{"id":"d2aertr7hcw0","created":1719451742539,"text":"RiotGame"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af0qawruw0","created":1719452440300,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ue4rhc0","created":1719452449202,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0v94src0","created":1719452451077,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0w3igvc0","created":1719452452914,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ws6vd40","created":1719452454406,"text":"赛事","layout_mind_offset":{"x":7.499999980131406,"y":-205.33332834773637}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af130z16w0","created":1719452467998,"text":"html","layout_left_offset":{"x":-9.166666156715792,"y":-14.99999916553503}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af1u1nh8o0","created":1719452526812,"text":".header: 头部区域，包含网站的logo、导航栏和下载链接"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af1xqokjs0","created":1719452534856,"text":".sidebar: 侧边栏，列出各个赛事的链接。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af208tt8w0","created":1719452540307,"text":".content: 内容区域，显示选定赛事的详细信息。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af17c4e200","created":1719452477379,"text":"css","layout_left_offset":{"x":-31.66666490501825,"y":-0.8333332869742662}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af4a438u80","created":1719452718516,"text":"选择器"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af4nha6m00","created":1719452747612,"text":"类选择器（如 .header, .sidebar）：用于选择具有特定类名的元素，并为它们应用样式。\n元素选择器（如 body, div, ul, li）：用于选择特定类型的HTML元素。\n伪类选择器（如 :hover）：用于在用户与元素交互时应用特定的样式。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-181.24999441827356,"y":-19.999999384085413}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af4dp77h40","created":1719452726323,"text":"布局和定位"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af5bio8ds0","created":1719452799939,"text":"Flexbox：在 .header 和 .teams 中使用了Flexbox布局模型，通过 display: flex 和相关属性（如 justify-content, align-items）实现元素的水平和垂直布局。\n绝对定位：通过 position: absolute、top, left 等属性，控制 .content 元素的精确位置。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-299.9999907612806,"y":1.1368683772161603e-13}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af4kcgz4w0","created":1719452740791,"text":"间距和填充："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af5jnjhd40","created":1719452817648,"text":"外边距和内边距：通过 margin 和 padding 属性设置元素之间的间距和内容与边框之间的距离。\n例如，.header .logo 中的 margin-left 和 .header nav ul 中的 margin-right 控制元素之间的水平间距。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-814.9999749014787,"y":38.74999880666519}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af182lzso0","created":1719452478981,"text":"Javascript","layout_left_offset":{"x":-13.333332591586668,"y":10.83333273066421}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af2414nsw0","created":1719452548548,"text":"document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() { ... });:\n 当文档加载完成后执行的事件处理函数，确保在DOM完全加载后再执行JavaScript代码。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-551.2499830238527,"y":38.7499988066653}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af29z9k800","created":1719452561496,"text":"const events = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar ul li');: 获取侧边栏中所有赛事的列表项。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2ci87c80","created":1719452566996,"text":"const eventDetails = document.querySelectorAll('.event');: 获取所有赛事详细信息的容器。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2f4fa4g0","created":1719452572692,"text":"events.forEach(event => { ... });: 遍历每个赛事列表项，并为其添加点击事件监听器。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af2hpu7eg0","created":1719452578340,"text":"点击事件监听器的处理函数通过点击赛事名称，在所有赛事详细信息容器中隐藏非当前赛事的信息，并显示被点击赛事的详细信息。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-524.9999838322406,"y":57.49999822924519}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0xghvfk0","created":1719452455876,"text":"首页"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af6orf0qo0","created":1719452907130,"text":"html"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7514xvs0","created":1719452942546,"text":"使用 <div> 元素创建不同的区块，如 .header, .image, .game, .image1，用于组织页面内容。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7abfh6w0","created":1719452954052,"text":"使用 <ul> 和 <li> 创建导航菜单，包含下拉菜单（使用 <ul class=\"dropdown\"> 和嵌套的 <li>）。\n使用 <a> 元素创建链接，将用户引导至其他页面或内部部分。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-624.9999807526679,"y":9.99999969204282}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af6qm2m5c0","created":1719452911160,"text":"css"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7y5lfaw0","created":1719453005942,"text":"布局"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7yxeaio0","created":1719453007624,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7zvx28o0","created":1719453009711,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af6rjaurs0","created":1719452913170,"text":"JavaScript"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2af7iibk680","created":1719452971883,"text":"在 <script> 标签内编写了 JavaScript 代码，通过监听 window 的 scroll 事件来实现滚动效果。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af7j9yroo0","created":1719452973555,"text":"scroll() 函数根据页面滚动的位置动态地添加或移除 .scrolled 类名给 .header 元素，从而改变其样式。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0y4blx40","created":1719452457316,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2af0ytlv1c0","created":1719452458845,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}